{"amendement": {"@xmlns": "http://schemas.assemblee-nationale.fr/referentiel", "uid": "AMANR5L17PO59048B0324P2D1N002373", "chronotag": "1739874556219", "legislature": "17", "identification": {"numeroLong": "II-CF2373", "numeroOrdreDepot": "2373", "prefixeOrganeExamen": "CION_FIN", "numeroRect": "0"}, "examenRef": "EXANR5L17PO59048B0324P2D1", "texteLegislatifRef": "PRJLANR5L17B0324", "triAmendement": "beoaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaacvzzqs", "cardinaliteAmdtMultiples": "1", "amendementParentRef": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "signataires": {"auteur": {"typeAuteur": "D\u00e9put\u00e9", "gouvernementRef": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "acteurRef": "PA795762", "groupePolitiqueRef": "PO845419", "auteurRapporteurOrganeRef": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}}, "cosignataires": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "suffixe": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "libelle": "M.&#160;Califer"}, "pointeurFragmentTexte": {"partieAmendableRef": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "division": {"titre": "\u00c9TAT B", "articleDesignationCourte": "ART. 42", "articleDesignation": "ARTICLE 42", "type": "ANNEXE", "avant_A_Apres": "A", "divisionRattachee": "ARTICLE 42", "articleAdditionnel": "false", "chapitreAdditionnel": "false", "urlDivisionTexteVise": "/17/textes/0324C.asp#D_Etat_B"}, "missionVisee": {"codeEtat": "B", "codeMissionMinefi": "OA", "libelleMission": "Outre-mer", "missionRef": "2880"}}, "corps": {"cartoucheInformatif": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "contenuAuteur": {"dispositifAmdtCreditPLF": {"listeProgrammes": {"programme": [{"libelle": "Emploi outre-mer", "programmeRef": "464610", "autorisationEngagement": "-3000000", "creditPaiement": "-3000000", "action": "modification", "lignesCredits": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}}, {"libelle": "Conditions de vie outre-mer", "programmeRef": "464612", "autorisationEngagement": "3000000", "creditPaiement": "3000000", "action": "modification", "lignesCredits": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}}]}, "soldeAE": "0", "soldeCP": "0", "cpEgalAe": "true"}, "avantAppel": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "exposeSommaire": "<p>Le pr&#x00E9;sent amendement de cr&#x00E9;dit propose de renforcer les moyens budg&#x00E9;taires d&#x00E9;volus &#x00E0; la prise en charge du Fonds Barnier.</p><p>Il est crucial d'abonder le Fonds Barnier, dans les territoires d'Outre-mer, car ces r&#x00E9;gions sont particuli&#x00E8;rement vuln&#x00E9;rables aux catastrophes naturelles. Les territoires ultramarins, situ&#x00E9;s pour la plupart dans des zones g&#x00E9;ographiques expos&#x00E9;es aux cyclones, s&#x00E9;ismes, &#x00E9;ruptions volcaniques et mont&#x00E9;es des eaux, subissent r&#x00E9;guli&#x00E8;rement des &#x00E9;v&#x00E9;nements climatiques extr&#x00EA;mes qui endommagent gravement leurs infrastructures, logements et &#x00E9;cosyst&#x00E8;mes. Renforcer ce fonds dans les Outre-mer permettrait de r&#x00E9;pondre plus efficacement aux besoins de reconstruction et de soutien, souvent massifs, apr&#x00E8;s une catastrophe, en r&#x00E9;duisant le d&#x00E9;lai d'intervention et en assurant une meilleure r&#x00E9;silience face aux chocs futurs.</p><p>Le pr&#x00E9;sent amendement op&#x00E8;re un transfert du programme &#x00AB;&nbsp;Emploi Outre-mer&nbsp;&#x00BB; au programme &#x00AB;&nbsp;Conditions de vie Outre-mer&nbsp;&#x00BB; afin de tenir compte des contraintes impos&#x00E9;es par l&#x2019;article 40 de la Constitution. Il ne vise donc aucunement &#x00E0; abaisser le programme &#x00AB;&nbsp;Emploi Outre-mer&nbsp;&#x00BB; d&#x00E9;j&#x00E0; trop peu &#x00E9;lev&#x00E9;.</p>", "annexeExposeSommaire": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}}}, "cycleDeVie": {"dateDepot": "2024-10-29", "datePublication": "2024-11-15", "soumisArticle40": "true", "etatDesTraitements": {"etat": {"code": "DI", "libelle": "Discut\u00e9"}, "sousEtat": {"code": "DI", "libelle": "Adopt\u00e9"}}, "dateSort": "2024-11-04T12:33:43+01:00", "sort": "Adopt\u00e9"}, "representations": {"representation": {"nom": "PDF", "typeMime": {"type": "application", "subType": "PDF"}, "statutRepresentation": {"verbatim": "true", "canonique": "true", "officielle": "true", "transcription": "false", "enregistrement": "false"}, "repSource": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "offset": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "contenu": {"documentURI": "/base/AMANR5L17PO59048B0324P2D1N002373?format=pdf"}, "dateDispoRepresentation": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}}}, "seanceDiscussionRef": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "article99": "false", "loiReference": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "discussionCommune": {"idDiscussion": "27746", "typePosition": "Milieu"}, "discussionIdentique": {"@xmlns:xsi": "http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance", "@xsi:nil": "true"}, "accordGouvernementDepotHorsDelai": "Sans objet"}}